.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, iced-tea
There 3 different types of food: plum, orange, lettuce
3 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, dubstep, ambient
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person eating lettuce is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking almond-milk##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person drinking almond-milk##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is the person eating plum##1
6. the fan of country is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Beverage    | coffee    | iced-tea | almond-milk |
| Food       | orange   | lettuce  | plum  |
| Pet         | frog      | fish     | goldfish    |
| Music-Genre   | country | ambient    | dubstep        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, car, trike
There 3 different types of food: corn, lime, pear
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat
1. the person eating lime is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person eating corn is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the bird and the person eating pear##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person driving the van is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Transport         | trike | van | car |
| Food           | pear     | lime    | corn |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard      | bird    |

