.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, taxi, jet-ski
There 3 different types of food: carrot, kiwi, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, november, october
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, nigerian
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person eating zucchini is between the nigerian and the person eating carrot##2
7. the person eating zucchini is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Transport      | taxi | skateboard       | jet-ski   |
| Food          | carrot   | zucchini   | kiwi     |
| Birthday         | november  | january    | october  |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian | nigerian |

