.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, parkour, rugby
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, pepper, radish
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, tulip
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, scooter, train
1. the person driving the scooter is between the person who's sport is golf and the person who's sport is parkour##2
2. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person eating pepper and the person eating radish##2
6. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
8. the person eating pepper is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Sport      | parkour   | rugby    | golf   |
| Food          | radish | eggplant  | pepper |
| Flower   | balloon-flower   | daisy | tulip  |
| Transport     | roller | scooter   | train  |

