.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, january
3 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, pony
3 different games are played: backgammon, go, snooker
1. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is the owner of the pony##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3
4. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the owner of the cat is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage   | 7up         | soy-milk      | lemonade   |
| Birthday        | january | may          | october |
| Pet        | cat         | lizard        | pony       |
| Game      | go       | snooker | backgammon       |

