.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, rugby, handball
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, paramedic, teacher
3 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, mouse
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, russian, nigerian
1. the teacher is the australian##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the fisherman is on the left or right of the russian##3
4. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the person who's sport is handball is the nigerian##1
6. the teacher is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Sport       | handball | swimming    | rugby |
| Job         | fisherman   | paramedic | teacher     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig  | mouse     | frog        |
| Nationality   | nigerian       | russian   | australian         |

