.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, soy-milk, water
There 3 different types of food: eggplant, kale, spinach
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, baking, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cycling
1. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
3. the person who's sport is climbing is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person eating kale##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is climbing##2
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is baseball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage      | water     | soy-milk | lemonade  |
| Food          | spinach   | kale     | eggplant  |
| Hobby   | woodworking       | fishing    | baking |
| Sport   | baseball | cycling     | climbing   |

