.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, photography, reading
There 3 different types of food: lime, watermelon, papaya
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, rugby
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, funk, salsa
1. the person eating watermelon is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person eating lime##2
2. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
4. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
6. the fan of funk is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | reading   | photography | fishing  |
| Food         | papaya      | watermelon      | lime   |
| Sport       | golf      | rugby       | baseball |
| Music-Genre   | house | salsa       | funk     |

