.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, pineapple, watermelon
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, poppy
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, drama, sports
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bolivar, montecristo
1. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the bolivar-smoker##3
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3
6. the siglo-smoker is on the far right##1
7. the person watching drama movies is between the person who growsdahlia and the person who growssunflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | nectarine | pineapple |
| Flower           | dahlia   | poppy   | sunflower |
| Movie-Genre   | sports     | drama     | disaster  |
| Cigar   | bolivar     | montecristo  | siglo   |

