.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, drama, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, august, february
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, puzzles
3 different pets are kept: bird, frog, goat
1. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in august##2
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
3. the person watching drama movies is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in february is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the bird##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller    | horror |
| Birthday       | august          | february     | april       |
| Hobby      | puzzles       | card-games | board-games |
| Pet        | frog          | goat       | bird        |

