4. the canadian is on the left of the colombian##1
5. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person eating plum##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Food   | cherry     | lemon   | plum   |
| Nationality   | canadian   | colombian | argentine |
| Game           | snooker        | backgammon    | go       |
| Sport         | basketball | cycling   | handball  |

