.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-17::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, helicopter, quad-bike
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, freelancer, lawyer
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, water-polo, sailing
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, rabbit
1. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
5. the freelancer is between the person driving the helicopter and the lawyer##2
6. the person who's sport is sailing is the lawyer##1
7. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Transport         | helicopter      | quad-bike     | van |
| Job           | entrepreneur | freelancer | lawyer     |
| Sport   | snowboarding    | water-polo       | sailing      |
| Pet           | cat          | frog       | rabbit     |

