.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-18::.
3 different pets are kept: cat, bird, rat
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, martial-arts, sports
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, surfing
City: boston, berlin, paris
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is surfing and the person traveling to boston##2
2. the owner of the rat is the person watching sports movies##1
3. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person watching animation movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person watching martial-arts movies##3
6. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
7. the person watching sports movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Pet      | cat    | bird        | rat |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | martial-arts | sports  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| City     | boston      | paris   | berlin    |

